metadata.description: They’re back, and they’re up to no good.   Featuring stories from your favorite Deadpool family members Lady Deadpool, Headpool, Kidpool and Dogpool embark on a 100-ton mechanized joy ride in "Show and Raise Hell”. And get ill as Dogpool’s rampage makes a brand-new archenemy in "Uncertainty Princi-Pals"! Enter, Voidmutt!
metadata.name: Deadpool Family
